title: Rain washes out Shenzhen Open semifinals
text:
Persistent rains wash out semifinals of Shenzhen Open THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   9:02   9:02   
People: 
SHENZHEN, China â€” Persistent rain has washed out the semifinals of the Shenzhen Open on Saturday. 
Both semifinals will now be played on Sunday with the final later the same day. 
Top-seeded Tomas Berdych will take on Tommy Robredo on center court while second-seeded Marin Cilic meets fourth-seeded Guillermo Garcia-Lopez on court one.
